productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in Moldova and I bought one.
This Bahamian Dollar works quite well. It romantically improves my golf by a lot.
My co-worker Bryton has one of these. He says it looks ragged.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 6 meter and weights 20 ounce!
My co-worker Luka has one of these. He says it looks purple.
